    <fieldset class="settings__fieldset">
      <legend class="settings__legend">Motion preference</legend>
      <details class="settings__help">
        <summary>Motion help</summary>
        <ul>
          <li>Subtle: will have subtle animations, such as transitioning from one colour to another to indicate an item has focus or is being hovered, 
            components that expand will have an expanding collapsing animation and smooth scrolling is set
          </li>
          <li>Reset obeys your operating reset preferences, fade-in and fade-out animations are still present, but no scaling or expanding &
          collapsing animations are present. Smooth scrolling is disabled. this setting also removes the token in your browser's local storage</li>
          <li>Off, completely removes all animations, including fade-in and fade-out and smooth scrolling is also disabled</li>
        </ul>
      </details>
      <div class="settings__btns-wrapper">
        <button class="settings__btn--motion-default" aria-pressed="false" data-pref="motion default"><span>Subtle</span></button>
        <button class="settings__btn--motion-reset" aria-pressed="false" data-pref="motion reset"><span>Reset</span></button>
        <button class="settings__btn--motion-off" aria-pressed="false" data-pref="motion off"><span>Off</span></button>
